OL,3,CPolice officer has gross misconduct
OL,4,Ccase to answer over fatal e-bike crash
OL,6,FA South Wales Police officer who was
OL,7,Fdriving a van behind two teenagers
OL,8,Fbefore they died in an e-bike crash in
OL,9,FEly, Cardiff, has a case to answer for
OL,10,Fgross misconduct, the police watchdog
OL,11,Fhas announced.
OL,13,FKyrees Sullivan, 16, and 15-year-old
OL,14,FHarvey Evans died after the Sur Ron
OL,15,Fbike they were riding crashed in the
OL,16,FEly area of the Welsh capital in May
OL,17,F2023 minutes after CCTV captured them
OL,18,Fbeing followed by a police van.
