OL,6,FA statement said: "Our investigation
OL,7,Ffound no indication of contact between
OL,8,Fthe police vehicle and the boys' e-
OL,9,Fbike immediately before the collision.
OL,11,F"We believe a police disciplinary
OL,12,Fpanel could find there may be
OL,13,Finconsistencies and evidential
OL,14,Fconflicts in the information given by
OL,15,Fthe officer which potentially breach
OL,16,Fpolice standards of honesty and
OL,17,Fintegrity.
