OL,6,F"IOPC investigators also concluded the
OL,7,Fofficer has a case to answer, at the
OL,8,Flevel of misconduct, in relation to
OL,9,Fhis driving and language he used in
OL,10,Frelation to the boys at the collision
OL,11,Fscene.
OL,13,F"We believe a panel could find that
OL,14,Fhis driving at the time was outside
OL,15,Fhis level of training and authority,
OL,16,Fand contrary to the College of
OL,17,FPolicing authorised professional
OL,18,Fpractice and the force's own policy on
OL,19,Fpursuits."
