OL,6,FThe police watchdog's second
OL,7,Finvestigation into family complaints
OL,8,Fagainst South Wales Police, which
OL,9,Fcovers a number of areas including the
OL,10,Ffamilies' treatment at the scene of
OL,11,Fthe incident, remains "close to
OL,12,Fconcluding," it said.
OL,14,FThere was widespread unrest in the
OL,15,Farea following the incident, with
OL,16,Friots breaking out. More than 40
OL,17,Fpeople have since been charged in
OL,18,Fconnection with the riots.
