OL,6,FIOPC director David Ford said: "Our
OL,7,Fthoughts and sympathies continue to be
OL,8,Fwith the families of Kyrees and Harvey
OL,9,Fand everyone affected by the loss of
OL,10,Fsuch young lives. We know the boys'
OL,11,Fdeaths have had a deep impact on the
OL,12,Flocal community.
OL,14,F"Our role when someone dies following
OL,15,Fpolice contact is to examine all the
OL,16,Fcircumstances surrounding that
OL,17,Fincident.
