OL,6,F"Our independent investigation looked
OL,7,Fat the interactions South Wales Police
OL,8,Fhad with the boys before the
OL,9,Fcollision, plus accounts provided by
OL,10,Fofficers at the scene and later to our
OL,11,Finvestigation.
OL,13,F"After a thorough review of that
OL,14,Fevidence and applying the relevant
OL,15,Flegal test - that a police
OL,16,Fdisciplinary panel could find the case
OL,17,Fproven - we have determined an officer
OL,18,Fshould face disciplinary proceedings.
OL,19,FIt will be for a police disciplinary
OL,20,Fpanel to determine whether the
OL,21,Fallegations are proven."
