OL,6,FSouth Wales Police's Assistant Chief
OL,7,FConstable Simon Belcher said:
OL,8,F"Following the tragic deaths of Kyrees
OL,9,FSullivan and Harvey Evans in Ely in
OL,10,F2023, South Wales Police made a
OL,11,Fmandatory referral to the Independent
OL,12,FOffice for Police Conduct to ensure
OL,13,Fthe matter received independent
OL,14,Fscrutiny.
OL,16,F"The force has fully co-operated with
OL,17,Fthe IOPC investigation and provided
OL,18,Finformation and material, including
OL,19,FCCTV footage and body-worn video.
