OL,6,F"We hope that the outcome of the
OL,7,Findependent investigation and future
OL,8,Finquest proceedings will provide
OL,9,Fanswers to the many questions which
OL,10,Fhave been raised about this case.
OL,12,F"Our thoughts, as ever, are with the
OL,13,Ffamilies and friends of Harvey and
OL,14,FKyrees and all those affected by their
OL,15,Fdeaths."
